Exercise 7: Implementing the Observer Pattern

## Aim

To implement the Observer Design Pattern for a stock market monitoring application where multiple clients receive notifications whenever stock prices change.

## Project Name

ObserverPatternExample

## Project Structure

```text id="po8d4r"
ObserverPatternExample
│
├── Stock.java
├── Observer.java
├── StockMarket.java
├── MobileApp.java
