## 5. Test the Observer Pattern

### ObserverTest.java

```java id="r4u8ye"
public class ObserverTest {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        StockMarket stockMarket = new StockMarket();

        Observer mobileUser = new MobileApp("Rahul");
        Observer webUser = new WebApp("Priya");

        stockMarket.registerObserver(mobileUser);
        stockMarket.registerObserver(webUser);

        System.out.println("Stock Price Update 1:");
        stockMarket.setStockPrice("TCS", 3850.50);

        System.out.println();

        System.out.println("Stock Price Update 2:");
        stockMarket.setStockPrice("Infosys", 1520.75);
    }
}
```

